♻️ Streamline super-agents command - remove Claude launching

• Remove automatic Claude launching from super-agents command
• Remove --wild flag (no longer needed)
• Now shows clear status and next steps for users
• Update templates with latest MCP bridge improvements
• Verified MCP configuration works with Knowledge Manager

The super-agents command now:
1. Initializes project if needed
2. Starts Knowledge Manager
3. Shows system status and clear next steps
4. Tells user to run 'claude' separately for MCP integration
